         </extensionElements>
         <text>SAP S/4HANA</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-79523B0B-1EC7-4943-A560-D2E6A7CD031D" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>1. If Product sub is enabled to customer agreement, then if original product is not available then BYOP will look to fulfil SOLI with alternative product, which will be updated in the SOLI if user accepts results.
2. Original product can be found in
Material entered field in Sales A tab of 
that line item.
3.If user has applied and saved Fixed Material, Fixed Plant and DNI flag to SOLI in real time, then in either real time or batch ATP, BYOP will adhere to these settings when determine CMAD.</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-813281C1-6978-402E-A77E-1420427BBB0B" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Logistics wrapper program will apply for 2DN model</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-6C08A7A9-ABF6-4EF6-97AE-C3C5CB2CBACC" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>SO2 process also applies</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-B7F0EE05-8C91-43C6-AA47-4A51E627A34E" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>There will be a manual escalation process (outside of nightly reprocessing) where a CBA can raise only critical orders (not everything)</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-433D8AEB-FFEA-42D0-8BBB-AB45E9A5DA44" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>There will be a manual escalation process (outside of nightly reprocessing) where a CBA can raise only critical orders (not everything)</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-DD9FAF37-7B17-4F2E-970D-B076FBF50B65" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>SO2 could be created up to 13 days prior to SO1</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-F97CA64F-30CF-4D38-9341-A7DD97E58902" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Either this Activity can be done manually or Automatically</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-9240E0DB-358D-4736-B81C-D8CDBFF693A8" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Either this Activity can be done manually or Automatically</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-F65FB008-C251-41D4-9BA3-9D620E5380DC" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Either this Activity can be done manually or Automatically</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-BBD03F73-F25F-4AAF-B07C-B54180D14EC8" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Either this Activity can be done manually or Automatically</text>
      </textAnnotation>
